     going through the motions.

18:44.123 --> 18:48.001
It's...yeah.

18:48.043 --> 18:49.211
Are you really
          interested in me,

18:49.253 --> 18:51.713
or are you just trying
      to get some street cred?

18:51.755 --> 18:54.508
Oh, I'm not going to get
    some street cred dating you.

