20:31.021 --> 20:32.147
Did you rent this place out

20:32.189 --> 20:33.482
because you were trying
           to be romantic,

20:33.523 --> 20:36.610
or because you didn't want
    to be seen with me in public?

20:38.111 --> 20:40.906
