         curly-haired woman

21:03.262 --> 21:05.430
that doesn't have to deal
      with half of the bullshit

21:05.472 --> 21:06.556
that the rest of us do.

21:06.598 --> 21:09.935
-Wow.
            -Yeah, "Wow."

21:10.477 --> 21:13.605
Hattie, have you ever broken
      through a glass ceiling?

21:13.647 --> 21:14.773
No, I haven't.

21:14.815 --> 21:17.609
