21:17.651 --> 21:21.822
You accumulate bruises
      that don't ever go away.

21:21.863 --> 21:24.032
My first five years,

21:24.074 --> 21:26.785
I cried myself to sleep
             every night

21:26.827 --> 21:30.747
because I didn't have
     any friends or any support.

21:30.789 --> 21:31.999
My family started
           giving up on me

21:32.040 --> 21:33.875
because my dream was
    taking too long to come true.

21:33.917 --> 21:37.004
So I'm sorry that you can't
       tell that I like women

21:37.045 --> 21:38.255
by looking at me,
         and I'm sorry that

21:38.297 --> 21:40.090
I have a white grandfather,
         but you know what?

21:40.132 --> 21:41.883
