         that I can't help.

21:41.925 --> 21:43.010
But you can acknowledge it.

21:43.051 --> 21:45.053
What do you want me to do?

21:45.095 --> 21:46.847
You want me to apologize
         every five minutes?

21:46.888 --> 21:49.224
I don't want your apology.
       I just want you to know

21:49.266 --> 21:51.143
that we're not fighting
           the same fight.

21:51.184 --> 21:53.478
-I know that.
              -Do you?

21:54.730 --> 21:57.858
Look, we don't walk
         through this world

21:57.899 --> 21:59.651
the same way.

21:59.693 --> 22:01.069
